 Introduction
 ------------

 Since 2000 the Amiga Arena makes a lot of Interviews
 with many developers from the free and Sharware
 Amiga base.
 With this Database you can read all the interviews
 from 2000 till 2003.

 Installation
 -----------

 You need only the Freeware Database "XBaze" from Rafal Kaczmarczk.
 See http://www.xbaze.of.pl

 Copy this Archive in the Directory Data from XBaze!
 (XBaze/Data)


 Features:
 ---------

 - you can open from the Database
   your Browser and Mail Programm via openurl.library
 - over 100 Interviews
 - You can read them direct out from the Base!
 - You can compare the Interviews from 2000 - 2003

 Enjoy and read what happend in the past and see
 what is the situation today!


 Regards Olaf Köbnik



